text: The Tasmanian Greens are the Tasmanian state branch of the Australian Greens, a left-wing green party in Australia. The Tasmanian Greens formed out of several environmental activist groups. It is the oldest green party in Australia and one of the oldest in the world. The party's leader is Cassy O'Connor. Category:Australian Greens Category:Political parties in Tasmania
title: Tasmanian Greens
